<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSchrodinger.2C_Erwin1946">Schrodinger, Erwin (1946). <i>Statistical Thermodynamics</i>. Dover Publications, Inc.. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0486661016" class="internal">ISBN 0-486-66101-6</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/20056858" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/20056858" rel="nofollow">20056858</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Statistical+Thermodynamics&amp;rft.aulast=Schrodinger%2C+Erwin&amp;rft.au=Schrodinger%2C+Erwin&amp;rft.date=1946&amp;rft.pub=Dover+Publications%2C+Inc.&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/20056858&amp;rft.isbn=0-486-66101-6&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Statistical_mechanics"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
